item.description: The Toronto Blue Jays defeated the Los Angeles Dodgers 6-1 in Game 5 of the 2025 World Series last night, at Dodger Stadium. The victory gives the Blue Jays a 3-2 lead in the best-of-seven series, putting them one win away from their first championship since 1993. The decisive Game 6 will be played Friday in Toronto, with Game 7 scheduled for Saturday if necessary
